Backpropagation — “Mistake Correction Phase”

Now ANN checks whether the prediction is correct.

If wrong:

It learns from mistake
Adjusts weights
Improves next prediction
=======

Same Basket Ball Example 🏀

After throwing:

Ball misses basket

Now what will you do?

Change angle
Change force
Try better next time

This correction process is called Backpropagation.
